title: Not Able to install league
body: Every time i try to download league i keep getting an error code witch is 1935, If anybody can help me please contact me.

replies.body: This error can happen when Microsoft's Visual C++ wasn't installed correctly or is having other problems running for some reason. I'd suggest trying to reinstall that package, which you can find [**here **](https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=21254) along with steps on how to install it.
